        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Adds SQLite-backed Workboard attachments, durable notification replay/advance cursors, worker log/protocol state, and board orchestration metadata/tools.\n- Wires the new Gateway methods, agent tools, plugin manifest contract, UI badges/event labels, nudge dispatcher action, and generated i18n strings.\n- Documents Workboard SQLite namespaces, permission split, orchestration behavior, and manifest-only attachment export.\n\n## Verification\n\n- pnpm test extensions/workboard/src/store.test.ts extensions/workboard/src/gateway.test.ts extensions/workboard/src/tools.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/workboard.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/workboard.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose\n- env -u OPENCLAW_TESTBOX pnpm check:changed\n- /Users/steipete/Projects/agent-scripts/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local\n- node -e \"JSON.parse(require('node:fs').readFileSync('extensions/workboard/openclaw.plugin.json','utf8')); console.log('manifest json ok')\"\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: Workboard parity for SQLite attachments, replay cursors, worker/protocol metadata, orchestration nudges, and UI visibility.\n\nReal environment tested: Local OpenClaw source checkout on Node/pnpm with Workboard extension and Control UI Vitest shards.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: Ran the focused Workboard extension shard, the combined Workboard extension plus UI shard, the plugin manifest JSON parse probe, check:changed, git diff --check, and autoreview.\n\nEvidence after fix: 79 Workboard extension tests, 56 Workboard UI tests, check:changed, manifest JSON parse, git diff --check, and clean autoreview.\n\nObserved result after fix: New Workboard data stays in plugin SQLite KV, cursor advance is write-scoped, attachments export as manifests, and the UI shows Workboard metadata badges plus the nudge control.\n\nWhat was not tested: Live Gateway browser session and Crabbox E2E were not run.\n",
